            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1659889657964-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Zest half your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Cut the <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>lemon zest </strong>and the <strong>golden panko</strong> – this is your <strong>lemony panko</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
